body_html:
I have the same problem when compile
bazel build -c opt --copt="-DSELECTIVE_REGISTRATION"
--copt="-DSUPPORT_SELECTIVE_REGISTRATION"
//tensorflow/contrib/android:libtensorflow_inference.so
--host_crosstool_top=@bazel_tools//tools/cpp:toolchain
--crosstool_top=//external:android/crosstool --cpu=arm64-v8a

I also see this with 1.11 when building selective registration for iOS:
bazel-bin/tensorflow/python/tools/print_selective_registration_header
--graphs="${MODEL_PATHS}" > tensorflow/core/framework/ops_to_register.h
